    <traceEdge id="TR-030" from="REQ-AGT-012" to="REQ-UI-013B" type="dependsOn">
      <notes>XSD schema conformance (REQ-AGT-012) depends on XSD schema validation (REQ-UI-013B) as the schema must be loaded and available for the agent to reference.</notes>
